# [Implementing Deep Research (Web Search) for Agents]

Provide the agents (Asan, Max, etc.) with real-time web search capabilities to satisfy the "Deep Research" and "YouTube Link" requirements.

## Proposed Changes

### [Agent Component]

#### [MODIFY] [loop.ts](file:///root/gravity-claw/src/agent/loop.ts)
- Add `googleSearch` grounding to the Gemini chat configuration.
- (Optional) Add a dedicated `search_web` tool if Grounding isn't sufficient for specific YouTube URL extraction.

#### [MODIFY] [index.ts](file:///root/gravity-claw/src/index.ts)
- Update Asan's system prompt to emphasize the use of his new "Research" tools.

